<Site title={"the batumi guide \u2014 rega rega"}>
<Fragment set:html={"<section class=\"masthead\">\n  <a class=\"masthead-photo\" href=\"#cats\">\n    <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604542031658-5799ca5d7936?w=2000&q=80\" alt=\"batumi old town\">\n    <div class=\"caption\">\n      <h1>the batumi<br/>we <em>actually</em><br/>recommend.</h1>\n      <span class=\"credit\">\u2014 our own<br/>local journal</span>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n\n  <div class=\"masthead-side\">\n    <div class=\"masthead-intro\">\n      <div class=\"kicker\">about the guide</div>\n      <p class=\"lede\"><b>caf\u00e9s, restaurants, beaches, wellness, nightlife, and everything for work</b> \u2014 a list of places we send our guests to, and would <em>hand to a friend without thinking</em>. not from tripadvisor, not optimised for clicks.</p>\n      <div class=\"stats\">\n        <div><span class=\"num\">127</span>places</div>\n        <div><span class=\"num\">+12</span>this month</div>\n        <div><span class=\"num\">2-3</span>posts /wk</div>\n        <div><span class=\"num\">100%</span>tried</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <a class=\"masthead-cover\" href=\"/guide/oyster-weekend\">\n      <div class=\"kicker-top\"><span class=\"stamp\">this week's read</span></div>\n      <div class=\"body\">\n        <div class=\"top\"><span class=\"dot\"></span>just published \u00b7 07 may</div>\n        <h3>oyster <em>weekend</em>,<br/>and how to find<br/>the best <span class=\"under\">coffee</span>.</h3>\n        <div class=\"meta\">\n          <span>4-min read</span><span class=\"sep\"></span>\n          <span>eat &amp; drink</span><span class=\"sep\"></span>\n          <span>by the bre team</span>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"arrow\">\n          <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M3 11L11 3M11 3H4.5M11 3V9.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n        </span>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"cats-section\" id=\"cats\">\n  <div class=\"cats-head\">\n    <h2>eight <em>worlds</em>,<br/>one batumi.</h2>\n    <div class=\"right\">\u2014 pick a world to dive in. each is <b>a curated mini-guide</b> with its own places, sub-categories, and a map.</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"cats-grid\">\n    <a class=\"cat-tile stay primary featured\" href=\"/stays\" data-cat=\"stay-live\">\n      <div class=\"top\">\n        <span class=\"num\" data-count>\u2014</span>\n        <span class=\"badge\"><span class=\"pulse\"></span>start here</span>\n      </div>\n      <h3>stay &amp; live</h3>\n      <div class=\"sub\">flats \u00b7 hotels \u00b7 long-term</div>\n      <p class=\"desc\">our flats, hotels we send guests to, neighbourhoods we live in.</p>\n      <span class=\"cta\">\n        book a stay\n        <svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 11\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M3 8L8 3M8 3H4M8 3V7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.7\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      </span>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"cat-tile eat primary\" href=\"/guide/eat-drink/\" data-cat=\"eat-drink\">\n      <div class=\"top\">\n        <span class=\"num\" data-count>\u2014</span>\n        <span class=\"ico\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M4 1V8M4 8C3 8 2.5 8 2.5 9V15M4 8C5 8 5.5 8 5.5 9V15M11 1C9.5 1 9 2 9 3.5C9 5 9.5 6 11 6.5V14.5C11 14.7 11.2 15 11.5 15S12 14.7 12 14.5V6.5C13.5 6 14 5 14 3.5C14 2 13.5 1 12 1\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span>\n      </div>\n      <h3>eat &amp; drink</h3>\n      <div class=\"sub\">caf\u00e9s \u00b7 restaurants \u00b7 bars</div>\n      <p class=\"desc\">our favourite caf\u00e9s, brunch spots, restaurants, cocktail bars and bakeries.</p>\n      <span class=\"go\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M3 9L9 3M9 3H4M9 3V8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"cat-tile wellness primary\" href=\"#\" data-cat=\"wellness\">\n      <div class=\"top\">\n        <span class=\"num\" data-count>\u2014</span>\n        <span class=\"ico\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M8 2C7 5 5 6 4 7C2.5 8 3 10 5 10.5C7 11 8.5 9.5 8 7M8 7C7.5 5 9 4 11 4.5C13 5 13.5 7 12 8.5C11 9.5 9 9 8 7Z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span>\n      </div>\n      <h3>wellness</h3>\n      <div class=\"sub\">spa \u00b7 baths \u00b7 yoga \u00b7 massage</div>\n      <p class=\"desc\">slow living done right: sulphur baths, massage rooms, yoga classes.</p>\n      <span class=\"go\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M3 9L9 3M9 3H4M9 3V8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"cat-tile nightlife primary\" href=\"#\" data-cat=\"nightlife\">\n      <div class=\"top\">\n        <span class=\"num\" data-count>\u2014</span>\n        <span class=\"ico\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M4 2L8 8L12 2M8 8V14M5 14H11\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span>\n      </div>\n      <h3>nightlife</h3>\n      <div class=\"sub\">wine bars \u00b7 clubs \u00b7 late spots</div>\n      <p class=\"desc\">where to drink late, dance properly, or find a wine bar with vinyl.</p>\n      <span class=\"go\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M3 9L9 3M9 3H4M9 3V8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"cat-tile experiences primary\" href=\"#\" data-cat=\"experiences\">\n      <div class=\"top\">\n        <span class=\"num\" data-count>\u2014</span>\n        <span class=\"ico\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"8\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.3\"/><path d=\"M8 4V8L10.5 9.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span>\n      </div>\n      <h3>experiences</h3>\n      <div class=\"sub\">tours \u00b7 classes \u00b7 day trips</div>\n      <p class=\"desc\">wine tastings, cooking classes, boat trips, day trips we'd go on again.</p>\n      <span class=\"go\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M3 9L9 3M9 3H4M9 3V8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"cat-tile move secondary\" href=\"#\" data-cat=\"move-around\">\n      <div class=\"top\">\n        <span class=\"num\" data-count>\u2014</span>\n        <span class=\"ico\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"5\" cy=\"11\" r=\"2\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.3\"/><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"2\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.3\"/><path d=\"M5 9L7 4H10L12 8M3 4H6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span>\n      </div>\n      <h3>move around</h3>\n      <div class=\"sub\">taxi \u00b7 bus \u00b7 scooter \u00b7 car</div>\n      <p class=\"desc\">how locals actually get around. apps, rentals, walking routes.</p>\n      <span class=\"go\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M3 9L9 3M9 3H4M9 3V8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"cat-tile work secondary\" href=\"#\" data-cat=\"work-remote\">\n      <div class=\"top\">\n        <span class=\"num\" data-count>\u2014</span>\n        <span class=\"ico\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\"><rect x=\"2\" y=\"3\" width=\"12\" height=\"9\" rx=\"1\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.3\"/><path d=\"M5 14H11M8 12V14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span>\n      </div>\n      <h3>work &amp; remote</h3>\n      <div class=\"sub\">co-workings \u00b7 cafes with wifi</div>\n      <p class=\"desc\">caf\u00e9s with reliable wifi, co-workings, and quiet corners for deep work.</p>\n      <span class=\"go\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M3 9L9 3M9 3H4M9 3V8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"cat-tile explore secondary\" href=\"#\" data-cat=\"explore\">\n      <div class=\"top\">\n        <span class=\"num\" data-count>\u2014</span>\n        <span class=\"ico\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M8 1L9.5 6.5L15 8L9.5 9.5L8 15L6.5 9.5L1 8L6.5 6.5L8 1Z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span>\n      </div>\n      <h3>explore</h3>\n      <div class=\"sub\">beaches \u00b7 old town \u00b7 parks</div>\n      <p class=\"desc\">batumi's neighbourhoods, beaches, parks and viewpoints worth a walk.</p>\n      <span class=\"go\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M3 9L9 3M9 3H4M9 3V8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span>\n    </a>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"stories-wrap\">\n  <div class=\"stories-head\">\n    <div><h3>longer <em>reads</em>.</h3></div>\n    <div class=\"right\">\n      <span>stories take time. we publish one every few weeks \u2014 <b>people we love</b>, <b>routines we keep</b>, <b>photo essays</b>.</span>\n      <span class=\"scroll-hint\">scroll \u2192</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"stories\">\n    <a class=\"story\" href=\"#\">\n      <div class=\"ph\">\n        <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521336575822-6da63fb45455?w=1200&q=80\" alt=\"\">\n        <span class=\"nr\">people \u00b7 03</span>\n      </div>\n      <span class=\"kicker\">mr. x recommends</span>\n      <h4>15 places by<br/><em>nika</em>, our<br/>favourite barista.</h4>\n      <p class=\"summary\">we asked nika from milevski to show us his batumi \u2014 where he eats, where he drinks, where he sends his friends from abroad.</p>\n      <span class=\"read\">read interview \u2192</span>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"story\" href=\"/guide/morning-in-old-batumi\">\n      <div class=\"ph\">\n        <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604542031658-5799ca5d7936?w=1200&q=80\" alt=\"\">\n        <span class=\"nr\">routine \u00b7 02</span>\n      </div>\n      <span class=\"kicker\">routine</span>\n      <h4>a morning in <em>old batumi</em>.</h4>\n      <p class=\"summary\">three coffees, a bookstore, two churches, the synagogue, and lunch at a place with no sign.</p>\n      <span class=\"read\">read routine \u2192</span>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"story\" href=\"#\">\n      <div class=\"ph\">\n        <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554995207-c18c203602cb?w=1200&q=80\" alt=\"\">\n        <span class=\"nr\">photo \u00b7 01</span>\n      </div>\n      <span class=\"kicker\">photo essay</span>\n      <h4>one day <em>in gonio</em>.</h4>\n      <p class=\"summary\">cape, fortress, a fish lunch, the only good beach south of batumi, and the trip back through the tea plantations.</p>\n      <span class=\"read\">open the essay \u2192</span>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"story\" href=\"#\">\n      <div class=\"ph\">\n        <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559496417941-fd6b9c34c4ef?w=1200&q=80\" alt=\"\">\n        <span class=\"nr\">deep dive \u00b7 04</span>\n      </div>\n      <span class=\"kicker\">deep dive</span>\n      <h4>why <em>khachapuri</em> is never just bread.</h4>\n      <p class=\"summary\">a small obsession with adjaran khachapuri \u2014 five places, five recipes, why the yolk matters and what we got wrong.</p>\n      <span class=\"read\">read essay \u2192</span>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"story\" href=\"#\">\n      <div class=\"ph\">\n        <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1493663284031-b7e3aefcae8e?w=1200&q=80\" alt=\"\">\n        <span class=\"nr\">people \u00b7 05</span>\n      </div>\n      <span class=\"kicker\">mr. x recommends</span>\n      <h4>10 wines by<br/><em>nino</em>, sommelier<br/>at 8000.</h4>\n      <p class=\"summary\">amber, qvevri, saperavi \u2014 nino takes us through ten bottles she'd open for friends arriving from abroad.</p>\n      <span class=\"read\">read interview \u2192</span>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"story\" href=\"#\">\n      <div class=\"ph\">\n        <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1545162033-ee5d77b56b22?w=1200&q=80\" alt=\"\">\n        <span class=\"nr\">routine \u00b7 06</span>\n      </div>\n      <span class=\"kicker\">routine</span>\n      <h4>a slow <em>sunday</em><br/>in batumi.</h4>\n      <p class=\"summary\">flea market at piazza, an hour at the sulphur bath, lunch with friends, naps. our protocol for a day off.</p>\n      <span class=\"read\">read routine \u2192</span>\n    </a>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"news-wrap\">\n  <div class=\"news-head\">\n    <div><h3>what's <em>happening</em>.</h3></div>\n    <div class=\"right\">\n      <span>news worth showing up for \u2014<br/>fresh from batumi this week</span>\n      <span class=\"scroll-hint\">scroll \u2192</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"news-scroll\">\n    <a class=\"news-card\" href=\"#\">\n      <div class=\"ph\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551782450-a2132b4ba21d?w=600&q=80\" alt=\"\"></div>\n      <div class=\"body\">\n        <span class=\"date\"><span class=\"pulse\"></span>tomorrow \u00b7 15 may</span>\n        <h4>cocktail pop-up at kava lova with vanya</h4>\n        <p class=\"summary\">one night only \u00b7 19:00\u2014late \u00b7 reserve via @kavalova</p>\n        <div class=\"meta\"><span>kava lova</span><span class=\"sep\"></span><span>boulevard</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"news-card\" href=\"#\">\n      <div class=\"ph\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559561853-08451507cbe7?w=600&q=80\" alt=\"\"></div>\n      <div class=\"body\">\n        <span class=\"date\"><span class=\"pulse\"></span>fri-sun \u00b7 16\u201418 may</span>\n        <h4>oyster weekend at pure bistro</h4>\n        <p class=\"summary\">fresh oysters, cava, cr\u00e9mant \u00b7 all weekend</p>\n        <div class=\"meta\"><span>pure bistro</span><span class=\"sep\"></span><span>chavchavadze</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"news-card\" href=\"#\">\n      <div class=\"ph\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1545162033-ee5d77b56b22?w=600&q=80\" alt=\"\"></div>\n      <div class=\"body\">\n        <span class=\"date\"><span class=\"pulse\"></span>sat \u00b7 17 may</span>\n        <h4>flea market at piazza</h4>\n        <p class=\"summary\">vintage, second-hand, georgian ceramics \u00b7 11\u201418</p>\n        <div class=\"meta\"><span>piazza</span><span class=\"sep\"></span><span>old town</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"news-card\" href=\"#\">\n      <div class=\"ph\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1493663284031-b7e3aefcae8e?w=600&q=80\" alt=\"\"></div>\n      <div class=\"body\">\n        <span class=\"date\"><span class=\"pulse\"></span>thu \u00b7 22 may</span>\n        <h4>wine tasting at 8000 vintages</h4>\n        <p class=\"summary\">amber wines, kakheti producers \u00b7 6 glasses \u00b7 65 \u20be</p>\n        <div class=\"meta\"><span>8000 vintages</span><span class=\"sep\"></span><span>old town</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"news-card\" href=\"#\">\n      <div class=\"ph\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540541338287-41700207dee6?w=600&q=80\" alt=\"\"></div>\n      <div class=\"body\">\n        <span class=\"date\"><span class=\"pulse\"></span>sun \u00b7 25 may</span>\n        <h4>sunday yoga on the boulevard</h4>\n        <p class=\"summary\">free outdoor class \u00b7 9:00 \u00b7 bring your mat</p>\n        <div class=\"meta\"><span>boulevard</span><span class=\"sep\"></span><span>near pier</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"pull\">\n  <blockquote>\n    we don't <span class=\"under\"><em>rate</em></span>.<br/>\n    we just <span class=\"under\"><em>recommend</em></span>.\n  </blockquote>\n  <div class=\"sig\">\u2014 bre, batumi</div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"mapblock\">\n  <div class=\"mapblock-head\">\n    <h3>everything we love,<br/><em>on a map</em>.</h3>\n    <div class=\"right\">\n      <span class=\"legend\">\n        <span class=\"dot\"><span class=\"sw\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></span>eat</span>\n        <span class=\"dot\"><span class=\"sw\" style=\"background:var(--teal)\"></span>wellness</span>\n        <span class=\"dot\"><span class=\"sw\" style=\"background:var(--yellow)\"></span>move</span>\n        <span class=\"dot\"><span class=\"sw\" style=\"background:var(--purple)\"></span>nightlife</span>\n        <span class=\"dot\"><span class=\"sw\" style=\"background:var(--ink)\"></span>bre flat</span>\n      </span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"map\">\n    <div class=\"grid-bg\"></div>\n    <div class=\"coastline\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 1000 400\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\">\n        <path d=\"M 0 380 Q 100 360 200 350 T 400 320 T 600 280 T 800 220 T 1000 160 L 1000 400 L 0 400 Z\" fill=\"#bfdaee\" opacity=\"0.5\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 0 380 Q 100 360 200 350 T 400 320 T 600 280 T 800 220 T 1000 160\" stroke=\"#7bafd2\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" fill=\"none\" opacity=\"0.7\"/>\n      </svg>\n    </div>\n    <button class=\"fs-btn\